<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: black;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 450px;
            margin: 40px auto;
        }
        p {
            font-size:19px;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .logo-1 {
            width: 110px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            background-color: #e4e4e4;
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .footer a {
            font-weight: bold;
            list-style: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer p {
            color: rgb(99, 97, 97);
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 20px;
        }
        .author-mail {
            color: rgb(5, 20, 153);
            text-decoration: underline;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .author {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .reminder-icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .payment-details {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #ff9800;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .payment-details h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #ff9800;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #666;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        .due-date {
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        .urgent-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .urgent-notice p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #856404;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Employee Pay</h1>
        <p class="author">Hi Admin,</p>
        <div class="reminder-icon">⏰</div>
        <div>
            <p>This is a friendly reminder about an upcoming payment that requires your attention.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>
                Please review and process this payment at your earliest convenience. Click the button below to view the full invoice details.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>
                Reminder sent on: <%= new Date().toLocaleString('en-US', { timeZone: 'Asia/Calcutta' }) %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>
                If you have already processed this payment, please disregard this reminder. For any questions or concerns, please contact the finance department.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p>
                Best regards,<br>Employee Pay System
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div>
                <p>This is an automated reminder sent to the admin. If you have questions or need assistance, please <a href="">contact support.</a></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Employee Pay. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>